{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1394818, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 273862, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "同学们，随着全国疫情形势变化，结合我校大部分学生已完成新冠疫苗接种等工作实际，即日起不再要求学生每日上报体温。相应地，学生的紫荆码状态也不与体温日报系统关联(即没有上报体温不影响紫荆码的绿码状态)。政策调整后，各校门、楼门的地点扫码和测温要求不变，测温异常者导致紫荆码变红的规则也不变。", "timestamp": 1617615560, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1394831, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 273862, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "？我一直没上报过", "timestamp": 1617615651, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1394842, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 273862, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "从来没报过", "timestamp": 1617615747, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1394845, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 273862, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "来源？", "timestamp": 1617615789, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1394847, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 273862, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 辅导员", "timestamp": 1617615803, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1394892, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 273862, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 不测温学生卡刷不开楼门啊", "timestamp": 1617616259, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1395057, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 273862, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我码绿的也刷不开门，草了", "timestamp": 1617618279, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 273862, "reply": 7, "tag": null, "text": "速报：不用每天测温了！", "timestamp": 1617615550, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1617618281, "url": "", "vote": {}}}